Extension: VhDir Practitioner Qualification

Official URL: http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/vhdir/StructureDefinition/practitioner-qualification Version: 0.2.0
Active as of 2017-12-08 Computable Name: PractitionerQualification

Context of Use

This extension may be used on the following element(s):

  • Practitioner.qualification

Usage info

Usage:

  • Use this Extension: VhDir Practitioner
  • Examples for this Extension: Practitioner/practitioner1
